有等多幾個鐘"},{"pid":"705e4cdd137e107a03b77ec8abff14c9cc08fa9f","tid":2489041,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T00:37:39.000Z","msg":"JF 地球來的人2.0？"},{"pid":"8c96e0e5b40c88fa94aea0729e03f68c98480af5","tid":2489041,"uid":265909,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T00:57:24.000Z","msg":"強行解讀<br />\n<br />\n最初係達明一派的&lt;&lt;十個救火的少年&gt;&gt;<br />\n10個各種原因走左7個, 淨低3個照去救火, 但救唔到仲死埋<br />\n跟住C all star&lt;&lt;集合吧! 地球保衛隊&gt;&gt;<br />\n其中4個搵返救火嘅初衷返黎救火<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wOmNSFi37PY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwOmNSFi37PY&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=703cc73a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wOmNSFi37PY</a><br />\n<br />\n返黎救火又點? 果三個已經死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kfs.io/album/global/112237384,0v1/fit/500x500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kfs.io%2Falbum%2Fglobal%2F112237384%2C0v1%2Ffit%2F500x500.jpg&h=0a46fe72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留下來的人張圖, 部機係地球保衛隊果部<br />\n插係沙入面, 應該係講死咗果幾個<br />\n首歌係講死咗嘅人同留低條命嘅人<br />\n<br />\n今日2021年4月15日<br />\n300日左右之前有咩特別日子同死咗嘅人有關?<br />\n暫時淨係諗到2020年6月15日紀念過2019年6月15日"},{"pid":"88d0a3d4df4809d896080bfa7d6b0b49bcc13f5f","tid":2489041,"uid":261006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db2ddd7037ca5ad48f73276f6fc5cab02f8b9e77","tid":2489041,"uid":4000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bae8247bc3e470eae1c719ff7bebc8ddd09ac6e","tid":2489041,"uid":200644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cc82ba1dcdb03d684c19b5d37ab021a453d5ebb","tid":2489041,"uid":219128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"無KKBOX  邊度可以聽？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"其他音樂平台都上咗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T22:04:09.000Z","msg":"spoify 同apple music都搵唔到"},"citedB